org.microtitan.diffusive.translator

Class BasicDiffusiveTranslator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.microtitan.diffusive.translator.BasicDiffusiveTranslator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javassist.Translator, DiffusiveTranslator

    public class BasicDiffusiveTranslator
extends java.lang.Object
implements DiffusiveTranslator
    Observer of the Loader, which calls the start(ClassPool) and onLoad(ClassPool, String) method of an INSTANCE of this object. These methods can be used to translate the byte code before it is loaded. In this case only the onLoad(ClassPool, String) method responds by inserting a MethodIntercepterEditor that is used to intercept method calls to methods that are annotated with @Diffusive.
    Author:
    Robert Philipp
